                        (Please make sure to use<br> 
                        Post Office Parcel service)</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-3 footer-column">
                    <h3>Company</h3>
                    <p>Company<br>
                        Notice/Event</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-3 footer-column">
                    <h3>Social media</h3>
                    <i class="fab fa-facebook-square"></i>
                    <i class="fab fa-youtube"></i>
                    <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
                    <i class="fab fa-pinterest-p"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
